description:
&lt;p&gt;Due to members of our team moving on we are looking for applicants who are reliable, patient and enjoys a busy and friendly working environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The job includes work in and around our Twin Theatres in the Sussex Eye Hospital and the opportunity to be a part of sight restoring surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whilst experience of hospital theatre work would be advantageous the right candidate will be given a full induction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a 24/7 department and emergency work is covered by an on-call rota which, after an induction period, the post holder would be part of.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Phil Harris&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Clinical Theatre Manager OPH&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address philip.harris3@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone numbe r01273 696955 ext 64788&lt;/p&gt;
